<font FACE="Arial Black" SIZE="7" COLOR="#000000">

<p align="center"></font><font FACE="Arial Black" COLOR="#000000" size="6">The Actor Model (2)</font></p>

<p>&nbsp;<font FACE="Times New Roman" SIZE="7" COLOR="#000000">

<ul>
  <li><font FACE="Times New Roman" COLOR="#000000" size="6">The actor model is at the basis of the object-oriented concurrent programming which is one of the most important paradigms employed to realize DAI (Distributed Artificial Intelligence)
</font></li>
  <li><font FACE="Times New Roman" COLOR="#000000" size="6">Actor-based languages are computationally practical; they can be efficiently compiled and implemented on distributed multi-processor architectures</font></li>
  
</ul>
